sentence: The following companies are expected to report earnings prior to market open on 01/26/2016.
Visit our Earnings Calendar for a full list of expected earnings releases.

Zacks Investment Research reports that the 2015 Price to Earnings ratio for JNJ is 15.66 vs. an industry ratio of 60.20.
